 League]]||3||0||-||-||-||-||-||-||3||0\n|-\n|[[2009\u201310 FA Premier League|2009\u201310]]||12||0||3||0||2||0||-||-||15||0\n|-\n! colspan=3 |France\n! colspan=2 | League\n! colspan=2 | [[Coupe de France]]\n! colspan=2 | [[Coupe de la Ligue]]\n! colspan=2 | [[UEFA|Europe]]\n! colspan=2 | Total\n|-\n|[[2010\u201311 Ligue 1|2010\u201311]]||[[AC Arles-Avignon|Arles-Avignon]]||[[Ligue 1]]||4||0||-||-||1||0||-||-||4||0\n|-\n!rowspan=4| Country !!colspan=2| Greece\n!213||27||53||7||-||-||64||8||330||42\n|-\n!colspan=2|Spain\n!75||1||2||0||-||-||-||-||77||1\n|-\n!colspan=2|England\n!15||0||3||0||2||0||-||-||20||0\n|-\n!colspan=2|France\n!4||0||-||-||1||0||-||-||5||0\n|-\n! colspan=3 | Career total\n!307||28||58||7||3||0||64||8||432||42\n|}\n\n===International career statistics===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n! colspan=3 | [[Greece national football team|Greece national team]]\n|-\n!Year!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|1999||6||1\n|-\n|2000||9||0\n|-\n|2001||7||1\n|-\n|2002||9||0\n|-\n|2003||7||0\n|-\n|2004||15||1\n|-\n|2005||13||1\n|-\n|2006||8||0\n|-\n|2007||10||3\n|-\n|2008||13||0\n|-\n|2009||3||0\n|-\n!Total||100||7\n|}\n<ref>[http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/basinas-intl.html The Rec.Sport.Soccer Statistics Foundation - Angelos Basinas International Appearances] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131031171143/http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/basinas-intl.html |date=31 October 2013 }}</ref>\n\n===International goals===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:95%;\"\n! # !! Date !! Venue !! Opponent !! Score !! Result !! Competition\n|-\n| 1. || 20 August 1999 || [[Anthi Karagianni Stadium|Kavala National Stadium]], [[Kavala]], Greece || {{fb|El Salvador}} || '''1'''\u20130 || 3\u20130 || [[Exhibition game|Friendly Match]]\n|-\n| 2. || 28 February 2001|| [[Theodoros Vardinogiannis Stadium]], [[Heraklion]], Greece || {{fb|Russia}} || '''3'''\u20133 || 3\u20133 || [[Exhibition game|Friendly Match]]\n|-\n| 3. || 12 June 2004 || [[Est\u00e1dio