ive]]}}\n* {{cite book|first=Carter Goodwin|last=Woodson|author-link=Carter G. Woodson|year=1919|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=U6sQAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA91#v=onepage&q&f=false|title=The Education of the Negro Prior to 1861: A History of the Education of the Colored People of the United States from the Beginning of Slavery to the Civil War|edition=Second|location=Washington, D.C.|publisher=The Associated Publishers, Inc.|lccn=68029024|oclc=1003200476|accessdate=April 15, 2020|via=[[Google Books]]}}\n{{refend}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category-inline|Benjamin Banneker}}\n\n{{Portal bar|Biography|History|United States|Maryland}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Banneker, Mythology and legacy of Benjamin}}\n[[Category:African-American culture]]\n[[Category:American folklore]]\n[[Category:Misconceptions]]\n[[Category:Urban legends]]\n[[Category:Legacies by person]]\n", "name_user": "Corker1", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200ePlan of the City of Washington:editorial change", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mythology_of_Benjamin_Banneker"}
{"title_page": "YEAR0001", "text_new": "{{Infobox record label <!-- See Wikipedia:WikiProject_Music -->\n| name         =  YEAR0001\n| image        =  YEAR0001 Logo.png\n| founded      = {{start date|2015}}\n| founder       = Emilio Fagone<br />[[Oskar Ekman]]\n| distributor   =  [[Kobalt Music Group]]\n| genre         =  [[Rap music|Rap]], [[Post-Punk]], [[Electronic Music|Electronic]], [[Intelligent Dance Music|IDM]], [[Alternative Rock|Alternative]], [[Experimental pop]]\n| country       =  [[Sweden]]\n| location      =  [[Stockholm, Sweden]]\n| website       =  {{URL|YEAR0001.com}}\n}}\n\n'''YEAR0001''' is an [[independent record label]] based in [[Stockholm]], [[Sweden]]. Founded in 2015 by [[Oskar Ekman]] and [[Emilio Fagone]], it is under an exclusive distribution agreement with [[Kobalt Music Group]].<ref name=\"Acquisition\">{{cite web |title=MUSIKBOLAG Kobalt i avtal med YEAR0001 |url=http://www.musikindustrin.se/2016/05/10/musikbolag-kobalt-i-avtal-med-year0001/ |website=musikindustrin.se |accessdate=23 September 2018 |language=Swedish |date=10 May 2016}}</ref>\n\n==Artist Roster==\n* [[Bladee]]\n* [[Team Rockit (musical project)|Chariot]]\n* D\u00f6d Mark\n* [[Ecco2K]]\n* [[Yung Lean|Jonatan Leandoer96]]\n* Merely\n* [[Nadia Tehran]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Vill spr\u00e4nga gr\u00e4nser \u2013 men hindras fr\u00e5n inresa i USA |url=https://www.svd.se/vill-spranga-granser-men-hindras-fran-att-resa-in-i-usa |website=svd.se |publisher=[[Svenska Dagbladet]] |accessdate=23 September 2018 |language=Swedish}}</ref>\n* Quiltland\n* [[Team Rockit (musical project)|Team Rockit]]\n* [[Thaiboy Digital]]\n* [[Viagra Boys]]\n* Whitearmor\n* [[Yung Gud|Gud]]\n* [[Yung Lean]]\n* Yung Sherman\n\n==Discography==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Catalog Number !! Artist !! Title !! Release Date\n|-\n|YR0001\n|[[Yung Lean]]\n|Lavender\n|2016\n|-\n|YR0002\n|[[Yung Lean]]\n|[[Unknown Death 2002]] <small>([[Reissue|Re-release]])</small>\n|2016\n|-\n|YR0003\n|[[Yung Lean]]\n|Marble Phone\n|2016\n|-\n|YR0004\n|[[Yung Lean]]\n|[[Kyoto (Yung Lean song)|Kyoto]]\n|2016\n|-\n|YR0005\n|[[Bladee]]\n|Gluee\n|2016\n|-\n|YR0006\n|[[Yung Lean]]\n|[[Unknown Memory]] <small>([[Reissue|Re-release]])</small>\n|2016\n|-\n|YR0007\n|Adamn Killa\n|Back 2 Ballin\n|2016\n|-\n|YR0008\n|Thaiboy Digital\n|Tiger\n|2016\n|-\n|YR0009\n|[[Yung Gud|Gud]]\n|Beautiful, Wonderful\n|2016\n|-\n|YR0010\n|[[Yung Lean]]\n|Hoover & How U Like Me Now\n|2016\n|-\n|YR0010MV\n|[[Yung Lean]]\n|Hoover\n|2016\n|-\n|YR0011\n|[[Yung Lean]]\n|AF1s\n|2016\n|-\n|YR0012\n|[[Yung Lean]]\n|[[Warlord (Yung Lean album)|Warlord]]\n|2016\n|-\n|YR0013\n|[[Bladee]]\n|Who Goes There\n|2016\n|-\n|YR0014\n|[[Bladee]]\n|[[Eversince (Bladee album)|Eversince]]\n|2016\n|-\n|YR0015\n|[[Compilation album|V/A]]\n|Bala Comp Vol 1\n|2016\n|-\n|YR0016\n|[[Yung Gud|Gud]]\n|Body Horror\n|2016\n|-\n|YR0017\n|[[Nadia Tehran]]\n|Life is cheap, Death is free\n|2016\n|-\n|YR0018\n|D\u00f6d Mark\n|Drabbad Av Sjukdom\n|2016\n|-\n|YR0019\n|[[Bladee]]\n|RIP Bladee\n|2016\n|-\n|YR0020\n|Thaiboy Digital / [[Bladee]]\n|AvP\n|2016\n|-\n|YR0021\n|[[Viagra Boys]]\n|Call Of The Wild\n|2017\n|-\n|YR0022\n|[[Yung Lean]]\n|[[Frost God]]\n|2016\n|-\n|YR0023\n|[[Ecco2K]]\n|GT-R\n|2017\n|-\n|YR0024\n|[[Yung Lean]]\n|Vendetta\n|2017\n|-\n|YR0025\n|[[Bladee]]\n|Destroy Me\n|2017\n|-\n|YR0026\n|Yung Sherman\n|Innocence\n|2017\n|-\n|YR0027\n|[[Team Rockit (musical project)|Team Rockit]]\n|Trippel Sk\u00f6rd\n|2017\n|-\n|YR0028\n|[[Team Rockit (musical project)|Team Rockit]]\n|Ambrosia Junkie\n|2017\n|-\n|YR0029\n|Yung Bans\n|No Mercy\n|2017\n|-\n|YR0030\n|Thaiboy Digital\n|SOS\n|2017\n|-\n|YR0031\n|[[Team Rockit (musical project)|Team Rockit]]\n|Team Rockit\n|2017\n|-\n|YR0032\n|[[Yung Lean|jonatan leandoer127]]\n|Katla\n|2017\n|-\n|YR0033\n|[[Yung Lean|jonatan leandoer127]]\n|Psychopath Ballads\n|2017\n|-\n|YR0034\n|[[Yung Lean|jonatan leandoer127]]\n|Toxic\n|2017\n|-\n|YR0035\n|[[Bladee]] + [[Yung Lean]]\n|Gotham City\n|2017\n|-